FT  19 NOV 94 / ICI criticises electricity prices
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
ICI, the chemicals company, yesterday criticised electricity pricing
structures following a 60 per cent rise in prices it pays for power since
the summer. It said the Office of Electricity Regulation had failed to
ensure reasonably stable and competitive prices.
