FT  19 NOV 94 / Gonzalez's allies accused
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Political scandals in Spain spread yesterday from the ruling Socialist party
in Madrid to its Catalan nationalist allies in Barcelona where Mr Josep
Maria Cullell resigned as a member of Catalonia's government, the
